ed topics stocksstock screenerindustrialsconstruction  engineering overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse prxgpk on otc markets group usd  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description pernix group inc incorporated on june   is a diversified contractor the companys segments include construction power services and corporate operations the construction segment includes preconstruction precon consulting services construction management design build and general contracting its markets include the united states department of state dos and other government clients and private sector commercial clients the power services segment includes operating and maintenance of power production facilities with longerterm contracts the company provides its services in a range of end markets including construction construction management and power operations and maintenance om services the corporate segment covers the indirect activities supporting the companys construction and power activitiesconstruction segmentthe companys construction segment includes both general contracting and construction management services with precon consulting the companys general contracting services are focused on its domestic and international projects where it has developed a global network of suppliers and subcontractors the company provides atrisk and agency construction management services on complex facility projects in the private sector across specific market centers including advanced manufacturing foodbeverage biotechpharma healthcare higher education and other general commercial mixeduse sectorspower services segmentthe companys power services segment includes plant engineering procurement and construction epc om services and build own operate transfer boot capabilities the company focuses its service offerings on small to midsize power plants as well as transmission and distribution grids and underground cable installation the companys om services include maintenance and operations engineering ongoing reliability studies construction management recoveryrebuild specialty services and rehabilitation the company upgrades existing facilities including the addition of new capacity or the refurbishment or replacement of outdated equipment at customer sites the company also provides start up and commissioning services in addition to its om services and epc the company implements projects through a boot model to enable its customers finance and manage their infrastructure projectsthe power services segment operates power plants in the republic of the fiji islands fiji and the republic of vanuatu vanuatu pernix fiji limited is a subsidiary of the company that conducts power service activities in fiji the kinoya power plant consists of over three phasedin plants located near suva the capital of fiji the vuda power plant located between nadi and lautoka is the dieselfueled power plant in fiji with an installed capacity of approximately  megawatts for a total combined installed capacity of approximately  megawatts the company also provides services for renewable power including development design construction and facility om services for hydroelectric solar biomass and other renewable energy sources » full overview of prxgpk company address pernix group inc  parkview blvdlombard   il    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation don gunther  nidal zayed  marco martinez  grant mccullagh  c robert campbell  » more officers  directors pernix group inc news » more prxgpk news related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialsconstruction  engineering prxg  stocks profile for pernix group inc your browser of choice has not been tested for use with barchartcom if you have issues please download one of the browsers listed here market data  bb solutions report a bug give feedback market market us canada uk australia financial technology  market data mark